value: Sparse in arid and semiarid areas of Australia with scattered trees

stronghold in arid & semi-arid zones, mean annual rainfall less than 500mm but seldom in waterless desert.Mainly in sandy & stony plains of inland drainage systems, lightly timbered with acacia & scrub;also over swamps, bores, waterholes.

subcat_descr: Bill length (sex unknown) - Nares to tip
